fields.name: PRESTONE
fields.title: Hiker Boots
fields.description: The Prestone boot from Dune will add edge to your footwear line-up. Resting on a comfortable low block heel and shaped with a round toe. It's fitted with a pull tab and secured with a stylish lace-up fastening.

fields.name: PILAR
fields.title: Leather Ankle Boots
fields.description: Forget hard and heavy, these are soft and light. This ankle-boot version of our bestselling Pilar has a casual-cool 70s vibe. Sporting chunky heels, leather uppers, stitch detail and a full inside zip for easy on/off.

fields.name: CLAUDIA
fields.title: Suede Ankle Boots
fields.description: Forget hard and heavy, these are soft and light. This ankle-boot version of our bestselling Pilar has a casual 70s vibe. Sporting chunky heels, suede uppers and a full inside zip. With a full shearling lining for extra cosiness.

fields.title: Buckle Knee High Boots
fields.description: A classic equestrian silhouette with a buckled strap on the topline our leather knee-high boots are a timeless style that will never date. With an inside zip fastening and a stretch insert ensuring a close fit on the calf.
